abstract: >
  Open research framework for Emergent Vacuum Response Theory (EVRT),
  including phenomenological modeling, simulation-guided analysis,
  residual-force metrology protocols, artifact-discrimination workflows,
  scaling-law studies, and reproducible experimental infrastructure
  associated with coherent nonequilibrium electromagnetic systems.

