  abstract: >
    A constrained phenomenological research framework investigating whether
    structured nonequilibrium electromagnetic systems may exhibit measurable
    residual stress-energy effects under precision experimental conditions,
    with emphasis on artifact discrimination, uncertainty-aware metrology,
    reproducibility, scaling-law analysis, and conservative interpretation.

